    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Marquito's Arcade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun and learn with this collection of educational games. Each one has its different sub-missions and gameplays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cell Works</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a cell. Learn about cell parts as you fight viruses, collect cell products, nutrients or waste, and explore cell organelles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/e085692cbff720e87b18acdd71eb43f2.poster.avif?t=1765473270\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/e085692cbff720e87b18acdd71eb43f2.webm?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/e085692cbff720e87b18acdd71eb43f2.mp4?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chemibot Helps the City</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exploration game. A robot meets people in this charming town. Help them mix or separate substances. Learn about chemical reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/67ce452759333000adf13567a3af4d0b.poster.avif?t=1765473270\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/67ce452759333000adf13567a3af4d0b.webm?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/67ce452759333000adf13567a3af4d0b.mp4?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gaia and the Weather Powers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about the water cycle and weather patterns. Help Gaia make it rain on the mountains. She uses her powers to modify the weather. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/eca7dae526a9e153f4a253465ef04492.poster.avif?t=1765473270\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/eca7dae526a9e153f4a253465ef04492.webm?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/eca7dae526a9e153f4a253465ef04492.mp4?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super Pizza Delivery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight pizza-eating zombies in a magical world. Deliver to customers and divide pizzas into fractions. Serve the zombies before they steal your pizza.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/8c5b9fea8e5949706074aaafd868fc86.poster.avif?t=1765473270\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/8c5b9fea8e5949706074aaafd868fc86.webm?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/8c5b9fea8e5949706074aaafd868fc86.mp4?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Itchy Earth</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about plate tectonics as you help some tough guys relieve pressure points on Earth. Hurry up or the pressure will build and earthquakes will happen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebuild the planet by dragging tectonic plates into place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore our planet and find out more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/d99889f74a0020f9fc04e05e6d2667a5.poster.avif?t=1765473270\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/d99889f74a0020f9fc04e05e6d2667a5.webm?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151860/extras/d99889f74a0020f9fc04e05e6d2667a5.mp4?t=1765473270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More games will be added in the future and it is expected that there will be at least 10 E-learning games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
